{"tid":2430093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"asia mile 分換取buffet","createTime":"2021-03-02T16:52:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T16:57:29.000Z","uid":159130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fb7502f42e09b1ad8f3a6c497c11cef7d7095b50","tid":2430093,"uid":159130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:52:23.000Z","msg":"之前用asia mile 分換咗酒店buffet,有效期2個月，點知之後禁堂食，完全用唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打去asia mile,佢話冇辦法,最多可以扣二萬分退返分（我換buffet只用咗三萬幾分），得返一萬分左右退返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問吓有冇人試過，唔係我唔想訂，咁禁咗堂食我點訂？有冇咩辦法可以要asia mile退返全部分或者再book buffet?<br />\n<br />\n唔該晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6273d9668c0daac1c7b9082e598997f325436d2","tid":2430093,"uid":164477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"咁勇book堂食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 退就應該無得退<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我拎哂黎換酒"}]}